model

Class Photo

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Photo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Photo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Photo is an object used the hold unique identities associated to a image. A Photo in an album is identified by it's caption, which may be nothing, its URL (type String), date (dateOfChange), and a list of assigned tags used for searching photos with identical tag to key association
    Author:
    Pedro Cruz
